  <heading>MOVT (table to scalar)</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Move 8 bytes from ZT0 to general-purpose register</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction moves 8 bytes to a general-purpose register from the ZT0 register at the byte offset
specified by the immediate index. This instruction is <arm-defined-word>UNDEFINED</arm-defined-word> in Non-debug state.</para>
